家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"絕對同意"},{"pid":"11a7809cac29c9c2a92c65432252c38cb825e084","tid":1507263,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1．13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=a3931d1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04wmZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04wmZVM.jpg&h=efdc3dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dacdf03bebac5abd5937fec62dcb1c304a468c2b","tid":1507263,"uid":150079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"香港獨立，時代革命"},{"pid":"856b330cef89df689d4f87bbe67bed1d9c9aef99","tid":1507263,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eZe_e0bmvv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeZe_e0bmvv8&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=d22620af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eZe_e0bmvv8</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n本來講緊既就係香港獨立"},{"pid":"e1038a976a6048fb25bd4c959454ea86b6b4b721","tid":1507263,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:36:52.000Z","msg":"每晚10點"},{"pid":"28b9f2c1a6d4f43385f7258ffbd9b3a242a7b8f5","tid":1507263,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武後勤全面升級！增力前線戰鬥力！</span><br />\n平價方便遠近兼用<br />\n<br />\n[重開]早排返鄉下打獵，見到成班小朋友淨係掉雜物/用碌竹去打<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506828\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我要地區戰人手一支！"},{"pid":"23e798b9203fec986c378d83baa231c715356858","tid":1507263,"uid":155246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"解放殖民，香港革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：昨晚，打響了香港革命的第一槍，這是敵方意外地為我們響起的集結號，令我們無比的惶恐與欣慰。敵方終於用槍聲肯定，我們是認真的。<br />\n今年是香港的成年禮。初生的華英共和國，遇上老大的蘇維埃王朝，注定要大打一場，之後各行各路。你有你鎖國愚昧，我有我開放聰穎。<br />\n所謂反對逃犯引渡條例修訂，只是香港建國戰役的藉口，我們無心保護在港的財閥富豪的家財性命，財閥富豪也無心保護我們的赤裸身軀，彼此漠不關心。我們只是慶幸在這個無事發生的沉悶世界，找到大打一場的浪漫藉口。我們慷慨地將憲政民主的香港，施捨給漠不關心的富豪財閥，一群躲在在高樓廣宅的政治乞丐。<br />\n不是時代革命，是香港革命。不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。我們從未統治過香港，故此不是光復香港，而是解放香港。敵方都為我們開了槍火，不要遮遮掩掩，要夠膽講出來。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解放殖民，香港革命。</span></strong></span>打完了，香港成人長進，立於強國之林。美國走進來，世界捲入來，做我們建國鬥爭的見證。"},{"pid":"a88efcfcae3d043bf0e1a158cdf3c506294c0d49","tid":1507263,"uid":286639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"[緊急]快啲快手入嚟send email<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fafcf78a9a21bcfdf8b88488e6362dbbaf15ed76","tid":1507263,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"用返光復香港先啦<br />\n依加首要係五大訴求<br />\n無謂咁露骨直接俾位人入話搞港獨<br />\n到時就會蓋過五大訴求"},{"pid":"a4081cc0ff544725bc64168c4a5981c755313396","tid":1507263,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akg2Kum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fakg2Kum.jpg&h=161a0787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVFbCPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPVFbCPm.jpg&h=400de2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puGx6HG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuGx6HG.jpg&h=3befbd57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDbqHf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDbqHf1.jpg&h=7afabd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooj4dnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fooj4dnH.jpg&h=4a77